2tsp mustard powder
2tsp water
2/3 cup soy sauce
2/3 cup canola oil
6 cloves minced garlic
1/2 minced sweet onion
1/3 cup toasted sesame seeds
1 knuckle ginger

Combine the mustard powder and water and whisk until thick.  Let stand 15min.
Peel the ginger and chop thinly against the grain.
Blend all ingredients in a blender and liquify.
